dc_title_s: Map of boundaries: Hugg and Clark Fisheries tract, lands under water granted by N.J., Pennsylvania Shipbuilding Co., and Haggerty's upland
dc_description_s: Map covers area from Big Timber Creek to Woodbury along the Delaware River. |Map shows the boundaries of "Hugg and Clark Fisheries" tract, boundaries of tracts of lands under water granted by the State of N.J., boundaries of lands of Pennsylvania Shipbuilding Co. and lands underwater pertinent to said upland, and boundaries of Haggerty's upland and lands under water appurtenant to said upland.
